3.	Explain encapsulation with following:  Implementation not required
Mobile Phone and Mobile Phone Manufacturer

Encapsulation:
Encapsulation is used for binding the data mambers to its member functions.
Encapsulation also hides the data.
for example
Mobile phone manufacturer produces the mobile phones with their design.The user does not know the functionality of the mobile phone.
For example if the user touches the option to see the version then the function get called.
example treat Touch be  data and phone be an object when the object is created then it binds the data to its   the function.
